                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7661" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">TEC-0116</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4437 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新天钢的绿色技术创新：从绿色冶炼到绿色产品</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Green Smelting to Green Products: How New Tianjin Steel Drive Green Transformation through Technological Innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许晖，王迎军，杨金东，王泽鹏，魏建</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南开大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新天钢钢铁集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">研发部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色技术创新；工艺创新；产品创新；创新战略；创新平台；2023百优案例；重点项目；系列4-4</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> green technology innovation; process innovation; product innovation; innovation strategy; innovation platform</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，随着《大气污染防治行动计划》、《绿色技术推广目录（2020年）》等政策措施的实施，钢铁企业逐渐从“高污染、高耗能”向绿色、低碳的生产方式转型升级。“双碳”目标的提出进一步加快了这一趋势，我国钢铁企业通过环境改造、流程优化、产品创新等方式开展绿色技术创新，推动企业绿色低碳转型和高质量发展。在此背景下，新天钢钢铁集团有限公司（简称“新天钢”）紧抓发展机遇、聚焦绿色技术创新，不仅顺利完成对渤钢集团的“混改”计划，更是成为我国钢铁行业绿色发展的标杆。本文从绿色技术的内涵、绿色工艺创新、绿色产品创新、创新平台建设、创新战略选择等方面梳理新天钢绿色技术创新的实践经验，总结归纳新天钢绿色技术创新的理论机制和内在逻辑。关于新天钢绿色技术创新的探讨能够为钢铁企业和其他“高污染、高耗能”企业的绿色低碳转型提供经验借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the implementation of policy measures such as the &quot;Action Plan for Air Pollution Prevention and Control&quot; and the &quot;Green Technology Promotion Catalogue (2020)&quot;, steel enterprises have gradually transformed and upgraded from &quot;high pollution and high energy consumption&quot; to green and low-carbon production methods. The proposal of the &quot;dual carbon&quot; goal has further accelerated this trend. China&#39;s steel enterprises have carried out green technology innovation through environmental transformation, process optimization, product innovation, and other methods to promote green, low-carbon transformation and high-quality development of enterprises. In this context, New Tianjin Steel Group Co., Ltd. (referred to as &quot;New Tianjin Steel&quot;) has seized development opportunities and focused on green technology innovation, not only successfully completing the &quot;mixed transformation&quot; plan for Bohai Steel Group, but also becoming a benchmark for the green development of China&#39;s steel industry. This article summarizes the practical experience of New Tianjin Steel&#39;s green technology innovation from aspects such as the connotation of green technology, green process innovation, green product innovation, innovation platform construction, and innovation strategy selection, and summarizes the theoretical mechanism and internal logic of New Tianjin Steel&#39;s green technology innovation. The discussion on the green technology innovation of New Tianjin Steel can provide experience and reference for the green and low-carbon transformation of steel enterprises and other &quot;high pollution, high energy consumption&quot; enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《技术创新管理》、《创新管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">绿色工艺创新；绿色产品创新；绿色技术创新模式；创新战略选择；技术进步S曲线</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
